<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>名人 - 人物</title><link>https://siftrss.com/f/LbvpaQbPYJQ</link><description>来自人物的最新名人新闻、采访和故事。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 01:47:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>布蕾克·莱弗利 (Blake Lively) 出席 2026 年 Met Gala，与贾斯汀·巴尔多尼 (Justin Baldoni) 诉讼达成和解的同一天</title><link>https://people.com/blake-lively-2026-met-gala-same-day-settles-justin-baldoni-lawsuit-11965255</link><description>5 月 4 日星期一早些时候，宣布“It Ends With Us”法律纠纷达成和解&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/XZDJxFjXIL3j4OTIQ8elCL3C_JQ=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/blake-lively-2026-MET-gala-050426-8945ab85b47145fdb665d2fb7e7f3279.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 00:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/blake-lively-2026-met-gala-same-day-settles-justin-baldoni-lawsuit-11965255</guid></item><item><title>布莱克·莱弗利 (Blake Lively) 和贾斯汀·巴尔多尼 (Justin Baldoni) 主演的《旅人》在审判前两周以令人震惊的方式和解了爆炸性的“It Ends With Us”法律纠纷</title><link>https://people.com/blake-lively-justin-baldoni-wayfarer-settle-it-ends-with-us-lawsuit-11891516</link><description>双方律师在一份联合声明中表示：“我们承认这一过程带来了挑战，并认识到莱弗利女士提出的担忧值得被倾听。” &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/rL3S3eIWgZxtd69G-GV1IbUvAw0=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/blake-lively-justin-baldoni-feud-timeline-split-020425-2c797f9ad2ad4f91ba7f0041ed941675.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 20:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/blake-lively-justin-baldoni-wayfarer-settle-it-ends-with-us-lawsuit-11891516</guid></item><item><title>布兰妮·斯皮尔斯酒驾被捕后承认鲁莽驾驶罪，并被勒令每月两次看精神科医生</title><link>https://people.com/britney-spears-pleads-guilty-reckless-driving-plea-deal-dui-arraignment-11964607</link><description>这位接受认罪协议的流行歌星周一没有出庭接受传讯&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://